{"tid":1642252,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突破樽頸] 作左首小學雞英文詩做外國文宣","createTime":"2019-10-09T15:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T17:30:56.000Z","uid":73573,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b495e128b784aeecf482cf6ea9c27527fddb29b9","tid":1642252,"uid":73573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:49:23.000Z","msg":"突然心血來潮，如果將口號寫成詩俾外國人唸口王會點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去各大文豪修飾，希望可以將佢傳去俾外國手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講咁多，吟詩:<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<ins>HongKong Texas are connected by a bridge</ins><br />\n<br />\nHere's HongKonger's little speech:<br />\nEvenif Hong Kong's being rich,<br />\nStill under Tyranny offered by a bitch,<br />\nThe end of tomorrow world's being reached.<br />\n<br />\nThougt not yet heart a threaten pinch,<br />\nStill turn on the censor switch.<br />\nBlizzard put its freedom into a fridge,<br />\nKneeing on CCP for making it rich.<br />\n<br />\nA Texasian gave a personal speech,<br />\nWhich waking up the CCP witch.<br />\nForce him to apologize which,<br />\nHe refused to turn on the switch.<br />\n<br />\nHongKong Texas are connected by a bridge,<br />\nName called the freedom of speech.<br />\nStand and fight against CCP bitch,<br />\nProtect same core value: The freedom of speech !<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fbc68884e9ee92a948e9996437c2e1949f66f5","tid":1642252,"uid":73573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"召喚大文豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462f92964ea956282e7abf99bd3577892edcde6d","tid":1642252,"uid":73573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:50:35.000